    "maxLoops": 15,
    "maxToolCalls": 7,
    "contextTokenBudget": 60000,
    "gdprDisclaimer": "GDPR Notice & Consent\n\nThis bot may process Discord text and voice data only after feature-specific consent has been enabled for the current channel.\n\nEnable text processing: /gdpr text 1\nDisable text processing: /gdpr text 0\nEnable voice processing: /gdpr voice 1\nDisable voice processing: /gdpr voice 0\n\nStored data is limited to consent flags, the disclaimer-seen marker, and any feature data required for enabled text or voice functions. Contact Bullseye on Discord for GDPR-related questions.",
